subject: NCAA Basketball Tournament (Women)
lead_paragraph: Heather Claytor, Italee Lucas and Jessica Breeland added 17 each as third-seeded North Carolina beat 14th-seeded Central Florida in the N.C.A.A. women’s tournament.
